name: TeamNames.net
overview:
TeamNames offers fantasy sport team names, and similar fantasy sport resources through its website.

Fantasy sports fanatics from around the world are able to browse through hundreds of fantasy team names, rating their favorites, and submitting their own names for others to vote on. Tools such as the random team name generator, and random team name selector provide additonal options to assist with the process.

TeamNames also provides a listing of many real worldwide team names, and some of their basic information. A Google Maps Team & Stadium Search is a powerful tool enabling users to browse and search for sports teams globally using serial satellite photography.

An online shop provides the ability for visitors to purchase personalized fantasy sports shirts, and a range of other personalised fantasy sports products.
